UPDATE courses_trainers SET description = 'Mohan Pothula is an accomplished enterprise architect with over two decades of experience designing, implementing, and managing large-scale cloud and DevOps transformations for global enterprises. He has led major modernization projects for financial institutions and media organizations, leveraging AWS, Azure, and Kubernetes to build scalable, secure, and automated CI/CD pipelines. His strong foundation in system architecture, infrastructure as code, and microservices design makes him a key practitioner in bridging development and operations through agile delivery models.\n\nAs an educator and consultant, Mohan emphasizes real-world DevOps practices that unify software delivery, infrastructure management, and automation. His deep technical expertise, combined with a strategic understanding of organizational processes, allows him to help learners master the core principles of continuous integration, testing, and deployment. In DevOps Foundation Training, he equips participants with the skills to streamline workflows, enhance collaboration, and ensure high-quality software delivery across the enterprise lifecycle.' WHERE LOWER(TRIM(title)) = 'mohan pothula rao' AND (description IS NULL OR description = '');
